title: Boyce Avenue Discography (Current as of March 23, 2014)
description:
This is Boyce Avenue's full discography as of March 23, 2014. It includes every 

album of covers and originals, as well as the "Live in Los Angeles" album. It also 

includes the singles "Your Biggest Fan," "One Life," and "I'll Be the One."




Subscribe to their YouTube channel.
